    <section>
      <p>Some instances of <sourcexml>text</sourcexml> contain <u>only</u> underscore (_) characters
                for displaying blank lines or horizontal rules. The number of underscore characters
                in such instances will vary. Instances identified as horizontal rules shall be
                converted as such.</p>
            <p>If <sourcexml>text</sourcexml> contains exactly 51 underscore characters, suppress
                and create an <targetxml>hrule</targetxml> in its place.  Also suppress parent
                    <sourcexml>p</sourcexml>.</p>
    </section>
